flowchart TD
    A([Start: Public Website]) --> B{User Action}

    B -->|View public info| C[Read announcements and advisories]
    C --> B

    B -->|Create account| D[Register account details]
    D --> E[Send OTP]
    E --> F{OTP valid?}
    F -->|No| D
    F -->|Yes| G[Create applicant account]
    G --> H[Login]

    B -->|Login| H[Login]
    H --> I{Credentials and account status valid?}
    I -->|No| H
    I -->|Yes| J{Role}

    J -->|Applicant| K[Applicant Dashboard]
    J -->|Admin/Staff| L[Admin/Staff Dashboard]

    K --> M{Application period open?}
    M -->|No| N[Wait for open period]
    N --> O[Check announcements/notifications]
    O --> M
    M -->|Yes| P{Already applied in current period?}
    P -->|Yes| Q[Open My Application]
    P -->|No| R[Start application wizard]

    R --> S[Step 1: Personal/School info]
    S --> T[Step 2: Family and contact info]
    T --> U[Step 3: Education/Siblings/Grants]
    U --> V[Step 4: Upload required documents]
    V --> W[Step 5: Upload/Capture 2x2 photo]
    W --> X[Step 6: Review and final submit]
    X --> Y{All required fields/files valid?}
    Y -->|No| R
    Y -->|Yes| Z[Save application record]

    Z --> ZA[Set status: under_review]
    ZA --> ZB[Save uploaded documents metadata]
    ZB --> ZC[Create in-app notification]
    ZC --> ZD[Send submission SMS]
    ZD --> Q

    Q --> ZE[Applicant tracks status timeline]
    ZE --> ZF{Status final?}
    ZF -->|No| ZE
    ZF -->|Yes: disbursed| ZG([End: Applicant Approved and Disbursed])
    ZF -->|Yes: rejected| ZH([End: Applicant Not Approved])

    L --> AA[Open applications queue]
    AA --> AB[Search/filter records]
    AB --> AC[Open application details]
    AC --> AD[Review profile, docs, and notes]
    AD --> AE{Valid documents/info?}
    AE -->|No| AF[Set status: needs_resubmission or rejected]
    AE -->|Yes| AG[Proceed status workflow]

    AG --> AH{Current status}
    AH -->|under_review| AI[for_interview or rejected]
    AH -->|needs_resubmission| AJ[under_review or rejected]
    AH -->|for_interview| AK[interview_passed or rejected]
    AH -->|interview_passed| AL[for_soa]
    AH -->|for_soa| AM[soa_received]
    AH -->|soa_received| AN[awaiting_payout or disbursed]
    AH -->|awaiting_payout| AO[disbursed]

    AI --> AP[Save status update]
    AJ --> AP
    AK --> AP
    AL --> AP
    AM --> AP
    AN --> AP
    AO --> AP
    AF --> AP

    AP --> AQ[Add review notes/deadlines]
    AQ --> AR[Write audit log]
    AR --> AS[Create applicant notification]
    AS --> AT[Send SMS update]

    AT --> AU{Disbursement needed?}
    AU -->|No| AV[Return to queue]
    AU -->|Yes| AW[Create/Update disbursement record]
    AW --> AX[Mark payout scheduled/released]
    AX --> AV
    AV --> AA

    AP --> ZE

    L --> BA[Manage requirements templates]
    L --> BB[Manage application periods]
    L --> BC[Manage announcements]
    L --> BD[Manage SMS templates and broadcasts]
    L --> BE[View reports, analytics, and exports]
    L --> BF[View logs: audit/SMS/QR]
